(325, 2, '2015-05-30 18:35:05', '2015-05-30 22:35:05', '[shareaholic app="share_buttons" id="17605417"]\n<h2>Live From The Annex is</h2>\nCo-produced by Laurie Murphy, Sasha Wentges and Brian G. Smith; ''Live from the Annex'' is a monthly cabaret series featuring Toronto’s top disparate entertainers in comedy, music and alternative entertainment. The series runs the first Tuesday of every month, from 8 – 10 p.m., at CSI Annex, in the Garage, 720 Bathurst Street, (just south of Bloor street), Toronto. Artists include an emcee, comic artist(s), sketch comedy troupe, a musical guest, and the series’ house improv troupe: Annex Improv’s, Brunswick Stew. The shows are broadcast live via <a href="http://www.Dailymotion.com/YouAndMedia">www.Dailymotion.com/YouAndMedia</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Please nominate ‘Live from the Annex’ to be considered on the ballot for </span><span class="s2">NOW</span><span class="s1"> Readers’ BEST COMEDY CLUB at <a href="http://bestof.nowtoronto.com/2015/nominees.cfm?category=155&amp;subcategory=1389"><span class="s3">http://bestof.nowtoronto.com/2015/nominees.cfm?category=155&amp;subcategory=1389</span></a>. Thank you so much. If we have enough nominations by June 12, we have a chance to be on the June 25 ballot. Hey, if we win, we can celebrate together with big belly laughs and rousing toasts to laughter and joy!</span></p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-05-30 18:35:05', '2015-05-30 22:35:05', '', 12, 'http://www.livefromtheannex.com/?p=325', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
