(471, 1, '2015-08-19 15:31:42', '2015-08-19 19:31:42', '[shareaholic app="share_buttons" id="17605417"]\r\n<h2>Live From The Annex</h2>\r\nLive from the Annex is co-produced by Laurie Murphy, Sasha Wentges and Brian G. Smith; ''Live from the Annex'' is a monthly cabaret series featuring Toronto’s top disparate entertainers in comedy, music and alternative entertainment. The series runs the first Tuesday of every month, from 8 – 10 p.m., at CSI Annex, in the Garage, 720 Bathurst Street, (just south of Bloor street), Toronto. Artists include an emcee, comic artist(s), sketch comedy troupe, a musical guest, and the series’ house improv troupe: Annex Improv’s, Brunswick Stew. The shows are broadcast live via <a href="http://www.Dailymotion.com/YouAndMedia">www.Dailymotion.com/YouAndMedia</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.livefromtheannex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/NOW-Best-Of-2015-Vote-Info.jpeg"><img class="alignleft wp-image-380 size-full" src="http://www.livefromtheannex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/NOW-Best-Of-2015-Vote-Info.jpeg" alt="NOW Best Of 2015 Vote Info" width="358" height="554" /></a><a href="http://www.livefromtheannex.com/wp-content/uploads/201504/NOW-Best-Comedy-Club-Live-from-the-Annex-VOTE-PLEASE.jpeg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-381 size-full" src="http://www.livefromtheannex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/NOW-Best-Comedy-Club-Live-from-the-Annex-VOTE-PLEASE.jpeg" alt="NOW Best Comedy Club - Live from the Annex VOTE PLEASE" width="346" height="617" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThanks for nominating Live from the Annex as one of Toronto’s Best Comedy Club experience. Now, please vote at <a href="http://bestof.nowtoronto.com/2015/nominees.cfm?category=155&amp;subcategory=1389" target="_blank">NOW</a>\r\n<h2>Purchase Tickets for the September Show</h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="width:100%; text-align:left;" ><iframe  src="//eventbrite.ca/tickets-external?eid=18183435144&ref=etckt" frameborder="0" height="214" width="100%" vspace="0" hspace="0" marginheight="5" marginwidth="5" scrolling="auto" allowtransparency="true"></iframe><div style="font-family:Helvetica, Arial; font-size:10px; padding:5px 0 5px; margin:2px; width:100%; text-align:left;" ><a class="powered-by-eb" style="color: #dddddd; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank" href="http://www.eventbrite.ca/r/etckt">Powered by Eventbrite</a></div></div>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-19 15:31:42', '2015-08-19 19:31:42', '', 12, 'http://www.livefromtheannex.com/?p=471', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
