(450, 1, '2015-07-30 12:40:49', '2015-07-30 16:40:49', '‘Live from the Annex’ is pleased to announce its Tuesday, August 4th line up. Guest artists include ‘Mumsical’ (Comic Artist), Sex T-Rex (Sketch), ‘Deadmouse, The Musical’ (music) and Our Horizon (CSI member profile) with host Brian G. Smith (MC), Annex Improv troupe Brunswick Stew and Lee Cohen (keyboard accompaniment). The show also features a special guest interview of Michael Rubenfeld, Artistic Producer of SummerWorks Festival. The show runs 8 p.m. – 10 p.m., and takes place in ‘The Garage,’ at the Centre for Social Innovation - Annex location, 720 Bathurst Street, Toronto.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.livefromtheannex.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Live-from-the-Annex-Aug-4-Comedy-Music-Artists-News-Release-July-30-2015.pdf" target="_blank">View full press release.</a>', 'August 4th lineup announced', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'august-4th-lineup-announced', '', '', '2015-07-30 12:45:53', '2015-07-30 16:45:53', '', 0, 'http://www.livefromtheannex.com/?p=450', 0, 'post', '', 0),
